org.apache.river.reggie.proxy

Class ServiceLease

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.lease.AbstractLease
      • org.apache.river.reggie.proxy.ServiceLease
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, net.jini.core.lease.Lease, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid, ID<net.jini.id.Uuid>

    public class ServiceLease
extends AbstractLease
    A ServiceLease is a proxy for a service registration lease at a registrar. Clients only see instances via the Lease interface.
    Author:
    Sun Microsystems, Inc.
